                <div class="tab-content">
                    <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-script">
                        <div class="js-script-content-wrapper top-margin-script markdown-content">
                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep5-forms/data-class-type-guessing.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Open <code>GenusFormType</code> and find the <code>configureOptions()</code> method. Add <code>$resolver-&gt;setDefaults()</code>.
Pass that an array with a single key called <code>data_class</code> set to <code>AppBundle\Entity\Genus</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="f53d936d53">
