<p>Actually, that's <em>kind of</em> a lie. These properties are private, so the form component
<em>can't</em> set them directly. In reality, it guesses a setter function for each field and
call that: <code>setName()</code>, <code>setSpeciesCount()</code> and <code>setFunFact()</code>:</p>
