<p>Technically, you could add a form field call <code>outOnAMagicalJourney</code> as long as you had
a public method in your class called <code>setOutOnAMagicalJourney()</code>.</p>
<h2 id="form-field-guessing">Form Field Guessing! <a class="headerlink" href="data-class-type-guessing#form-field-guessing" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Head back to your browser, highlight the URL and hit enter. This just made a GET
request, which skipped form processing and just rendered the template.</p>
