</p>
<p>So, it tries to render this as a select drop-down of sub families. That's amazing,
because it's <em>exactly</em> what we want.</p>
<p>But, it needs to be able to turn a <code>SubFamily</code> object into a string so it can render
the text for each option in the select. That's the source of the error.</p>
<p>To help it, add a <code>public function __toString()</code> to the <code>SubFamily</code> class:</p>
